sql:

FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_info mi
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.kind_id  >  3 AND t.production_year  <  2011 AND ci.person_id  =  922598 AND ci.role_id  >  2
